 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登班ON9自已就退埋場, 話去少次有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙重標準到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我淨是知勇武出席率一定多過連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自已有藉口唔去集會, 就唔比 「部份」勇武退下火線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821c3ff13ad3fb37e54a907c96da56222b9166bf","tid":1819663,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4a6f22daa87306c5922d36859f93153d5fad479","tid":1819663,"uid":110583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2e9a8f222ca689f90c9752ba77923aa690a315","tid":1819663,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1TXqYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1TXqYk.jpg&h=00f211d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"407a846a90e44839cb813c41f09329a8182e157a","tid":1819663,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034002cafba172ba920244ccb428a254762c492c","tid":1819663,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwn5zh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnwn5zh3.jpg&h=40b32e96&